Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:26.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Please my god tell me what should I do
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:42.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}誰かが差し伸べた手を振り解いて進む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:48.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}自由な不自由蔓延る場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:50.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}何かに追われるように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:53.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不規則な毎日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:59.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}信じ続けた真実も分からんなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:04.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}何が本当の幸せなんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:09.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}その答え知る者なんどここには居ない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:10.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Where is my god
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:16.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}荒れ果てた夢が眠る大地で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:22.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}死んだように生きるなんで　僕にはできなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:27.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}生まれたままで　今　光を秘めしい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:33.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}最後の希望　そして奇跡もう一度世界に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:38.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}輝きを放て
Comment: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:26.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Please my god tell me what should I do
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:42.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}甩開伸向自己的援助之手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:48.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}獨自前行在這所謂自由的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:50.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}彷彿在被什麼追趕著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:53.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}無常的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:59.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}堅信至今的真實也變得模糊不清
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:04.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}到底什麼才是真正幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:09.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}這裡沒有人知道答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:10.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Where is my god
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:16.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}在這片沉睡著夢想的荒涼大地上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:22.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我無法如同行屍走肉般的活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:27.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我要如同剛出生般 現在 孕育光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:33.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}孕育最後的希望 然後奇蹟會再一次降臨於世
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:38.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}綻放光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:04.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}終わらないメロディーを 歌いだしました
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:12.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}とても大好きで 少し切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.99,0:22:17.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}でも 止まることが出来なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:20.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}嫌いになりました
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:29.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}たとえ大切な君のそばでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:34.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Life on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.69,0:22:45.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}見える景色は　同じには出来ないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:57.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}心も未来も笑顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:04.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}そうまだ見ぬ愛も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:07.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:11.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.17,0:23:15.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}You know what you wanna be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:17.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}わかってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.74,0:23:21.42,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}I can believe you tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:25.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}You see one light for it tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:28.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}永遠と儚さと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.35,0:23:35.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}震える夜もあるけれど
Comment: 0,0:23:29.32,0:23:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:04.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我唱起了這無盡的的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:12.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我好喜歡你 但心裡卻有些酸澀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.99,0:22:17.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}但是 我卻無法停止這份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:20.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}開始有些厭煩自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:29.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}就算在最重要的你的身旁
Comment: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:34.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Life on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.69,0:22:45.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}但我們眼中所看到的景色卻並不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:57.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}無論是心意 未來 笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:04.22,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}還是那未曽見過的愛
Comment: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:07.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Sweet love in love world
Comment: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:11.77,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Sweet love in love world
Comment: 0,0:23:12.17,0:23:15.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}You know what you wanna be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:17.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我早就明白了
Comment: 0,0:23:17.74,0:23:21.42,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}I can believe you tonight
Comment: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:25.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}You see one light for it tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:28.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}雖然會有永遠與虛幻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.35,0:23:35.53,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}也會有害怕孤獨的夜晚
